titles.title: There is none like unto thee

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
D
Who is like unto Thee
O Lord among the gods
Who is like unto Thee
Glorious in holiness
Fearful in praises
Doing wondrous things
Who is like unto Thee
(Psalms 86:8)
